{"tid":998634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報導聾啞婆婆突能說話 中國媒體挨轟造假","createTime":"2019-01-28T06:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T06:22:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d5d75e85795fa5025acbb1018973d9ac447b1a","tid":998634,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpELQgUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpELQgUU.jpg&h=43fde1bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpDNKTbV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpDNKTbV.jpg&h=7912a92b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日前中國河南《漯河日報》刊登一則有關孝順媳婦的報導，不過內文中出現聾啞人士說話的情節，遭讀者抓出紕漏，更發現在紕漏消息傳出後，該媒體將報導一改再改，被民眾批是假新聞，對此《漯河日報》也發出聲明致歉。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，據微博上的截圖，該則有關孝順報導的文章名為「善良心靈綻『金花』」，文中描述一位媳婦王金花親力親為的照顧聾啞婆婆，但婆婆卻回應：「兒媳婦對我比親生女兒還要好，有這樣的好兒媳，是我前世修來的福。」<br />\n<br />\n文中多有為人詬病的地方，還有「無論婆婆『說什麼』，王金花從不生氣」等不合理的地方，此文一出引起不少中國網友砲轟，有人指出，紕漏被抓出來後《漯河日報》更是將報導一改再改，一下稱婆婆為「瘖啞人」，一下則改為「聾人」，最後乾脆把不妥的字句一併刪除。<br />\n<br />\n網友怒批「瘖啞人竟會說話，難道是有神蹟嗎？」、「編故事的水平太差了，還不如小朋友」，不過有網友出面緩頰，表示說不定婆婆是用微信說的。<br />\n<br />\n對此《漯河日報》在25日發出道歉聲明，表示會查明原因，並按規定對相關人員進行懲處，並對王金花及其家屬致歉，也對讀者的指正表示感謝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2685275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2685275&d=%2B6PerixXDkZX5A3TLqthDtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=493fb18d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2685275&h=b07ff2d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2685275</a>"},{"pid":"3805aad97000c864c4c8a4d89323a9c5dfe80b64","tid":998634,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"正常人都唔會睇／信中國媒體啦吓話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe09f9281fdc70483ecad66f55da8dbd8ed1b8f3","tid":998634,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54003d227dd9641c445ea13ac85f49c964649eda","tid":998634,"uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3805aad97000c864c4c8a4d89323a9c5dfe80b64","tid":998634,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"正常人都唔會睇／信中國媒體啦吓話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:22:15.000Z","msg":"大陸人仲有咩睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zGoDao.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zGoDao.png&h=34c6f4bb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}